Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 杀掉第三个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟紧声纳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找~到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你刚才杀了平民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止 这是第几人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 怎么这种地方都有啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃来逃去烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用声纳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该已经躲起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好啊笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 这游戏没有会输的预感
