Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真的吧 这就二十连胜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是轻松啊 SAKAMOTO(坂本)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真说得出口 还不是全靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害变四星了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然世界第十了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩BTOOOM能打得过我们的日本人一个都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这以后只能和国外的强手打要不升不了排名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着说着 又有新的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界第二的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:03:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好! 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 世界第一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BTOOOM 全世界销量高达三百万的这个游戏中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有枪之类的 只有炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有计划的 熟练地运用八种BIM炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不被发现的情况下 用声纳找到对方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是这个游戏的获胜要点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BTOOOM——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了 SAKAMOTO(坂本)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不比世界第二差哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们可是要成为世界第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了22岁还未就业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得过且过就是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这被称之为BTOOOM的网络游戏的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都受尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连结婚都结了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这只是限于游戏这个假想现实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还没意识到 我只是逃入这个令人惬意的异空间里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落伞?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 掉不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁 有谁在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么什么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确当时是在房间里玩BTOOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流血了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知道的时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在服务区内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不会痛也没有异样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是被ufo劫走...也没这样的可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的背包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱包还在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替换的衣服也有 是出远门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店的塑料袋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当也有 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之还是要先搞清楚这里是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来跑到了相当南方的地区来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要省一点喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这虫子怎么这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一个南方的森林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是哪

Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做了我的履历表给你打工的超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会去那种地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自己想做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做多余的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去老家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是坂本龙太吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想起来一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候被谁给叫住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算勉强让自己回忆起来头就会疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好买了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个包包没有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁放进我的包里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 好像按到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种不好的预感...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全部是炸弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种东西会在我的包里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我在现实中玩BTOOOM么

Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩现实的BTOOOM?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有可能么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱逃你这胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃了么 BTOOOM中最基本的技巧就是好好地躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲得掉的才会成为赢...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追过来了 为什么知道我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能硬着头皮上了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要真被这东西炸到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 现在不是考虑这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不反击 还在贯彻人道主义么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 哑弹么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚不是有爆炸么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 开关 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险好险 那家伙臂力不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再拉开点距离才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没爆炸么 开什么玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 现在才爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子 连炸弹怎么用都不知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么用的 没有说明书什么的么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 又跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动 回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么袭击我 这里究竟是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这颗炸弹 手上的这块玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是知道BTOOOM这个网游么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是迟钝啊 居然什么都不记得了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连炸弹的使用方法都不知道 还好意思逼我么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑掉大牙了 我才不会死的安心明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去 又失手了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我非要这样遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也是普通的日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好说一下的话至少可以绕我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.69,0:15:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了 我投降 求你放过我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 要死在这里了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跑哪去了 应该还没死 快给我滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 感觉得到 我能感觉到那家伙就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这个 跟BTOOOM里面的雷达一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话即使躲起来也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 又没中么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该就躲在这附近没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有雷达的话 躲起来也没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么我的炸弹会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候有数字!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是计时式么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么到现在才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的炸弹在BTOOOM中就是触碰式炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹冲撞到物体的同时随即爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的则是计时式炸弹 按下开关后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒数计时为0的时候才爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是跟BTOOOM设定一样么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是世界排名第十的队伍中的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是用计时式我也要把那家伙干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 如果这是游戏的话 是游戏的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实是这是现实世界么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪门子世界第十啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是模拟世界的虚名而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你藏在岩石缝这事儿早就暴露无遗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没暴露 趁着会儿把他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那家伙躲在那边草丛中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会从背后偷袭我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么好烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边一起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 你以为你能潜多久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一探出来就再扔一发!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7 6 5 4 3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不杀了他的话 就被杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是正当防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没做错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取这个 然后用这些炸弹活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直和网游一样的杀人游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在现实中"玩"这个游戏么

Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 饭田前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就和你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来这里工作的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再等等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司还有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在玩游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 别擅自进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲过门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 坂本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和妈妈吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦啊 气氛都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在线的时候别烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你的就职问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈亲戚的和叔说过了 能不能照顾下龙太
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.72,0:22:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和叔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在叔叔在开乌冬面店
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想干的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然这么说 但是已经两年没工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说想进电视游戏的公司这样的梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止 找份安定的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不是现在说也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈一直在为你着想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 现在给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:22:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 这里才是现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.02,0:23:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来昨天吃的都吐了

Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被带到这座岛来是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不能回去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.79,0:24:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算是那样我也
